26. Qxf2 Rxf2 {[%cal Gf2h2]} 27. Rh1 d5 $19 {This endgame is winning for Black.
}) 23... Rxg3 24. Qxg3 a4 $19 {[%cal Ga4a3] This position is hopeless for
White.} *

