Qb6 13. fxe6 (13. Nxc6 Bxc6 $1 14. Kb1 b4 15. Ne2 e5 16. Ng3 h5 {Transposing
to the main line of Richter-Rauzer variation.}) 13... fxe6 14. Nxc6 (14. Nce2
h5 {[%cal Gf8h6] Black intends to play ...Bh6.} 15. Kb1 Bh6 16. Qe1 Ke7 {
The safest square for the black king} 17. Nxc6+ Qxc6 $1 18. Nd4 Qc5 19. Qf2 (
