Qc5 18. Rhf1 {This logical move is not enough for advantage.} (18. Qf4 Qe5 19.
Qf2 Bg7 20. Nd4 $1 f5 21. exf5 Qxd4 22. Qxd4 Bxd4 23. Be4 d5 24. fxe6 Bxe6 25.
Bg6+ Ke7 26. Rxd4 Rag8 27. Bd3 a5 28. Re1 Kd6 29. Rf4 $14 {[%cal Gf4f6] This
