34. c3 Bd6 $1 35. Rg7+ Kb6 36. Nd7+ Kc6 37. Nf6 Be5 38. Rg6 Bxf6 39. Rxf6+ Kd7
40. Rh6 Rf8 41. Rxh5 Kd6 $44 {[%cal Gf8f2] Black's compensation is enough for
