$1 (24. Nxh5 Rh8 25. Nf4 Rxh2 26. Ng6+ Kd8 27. Rh1 Rxh1 28. Qxh1 Kc7 $13) 24...
Qg5 25. Rf3 $14 {[%cal Gh2h4] White is ready to play h4 and has better chances.
}) 23... Rg4 24. Qf1 Rf8 25. Nf4 Bxf4 26. Rxf4 (26. gxf4 Rfg8 {[%cal Gg4g1]
