In this position White has many options. The most popular continuation is 10.
Bxf6. This chapter will cover less popular options for White.} 10. Qe1 {
[%cal Gd4c6,Ge4e5] This is a typical move which we have seen many times,
threatening to capture Nxc6 and then push e5.} (10. Bxb5 $2 {does not work
