Rdf1 Qg5 23. Qf2 Qe5 $132 {[%cal Ga5a4,Ga4a3] The plan is to push ...a5-a4-a3
to occupy the dark-squares and weaken the White king's position.}) 22... hxg4
23. Rxg4 Rf7 24. e5 $5 {With this typical pawn sacrifice White both wants to
