17. Ne2 a5 18. fxe6 (18. Nf4 $6 e5 19. Nd5 Bxd5 20. exd5 a4 {[%cal Ga4a3,Gh7h5]
} 21. Qe2 {[%cal Gd3b5,Gb5c6] White wants to improve the position of the
