30. Qd8 Rd7 31. Rxd7 Nxd7 32. a4 Nc5 $17 {Black is clearly better.}) 21... b4
$15 {Black first threatened to play ....Nb4 to provoke White to push a3 and
now exploitats this weakness by pushing ...b4. Black is better.}) 16... h5 {
