[%cal Gf8g7,Gd7e8,Gc8b8,Ga5a4]}) 19... a5 20. Rh3 Ne7 21. Nxe7 (21. Nxf6 Bg7
22. Nxh5 (22. Nxd7+ $2 Qxd7 23. Qxa5 Nxf5 $17 {Black is much better.}) 22...
Bxf5 23. Bxf5 Nxf5 24. g4 Rxh5 25. Rxh5 Nd4 26. Rc1 b4 $15 {The position is
complex but Black's chances are better.}) 21... Qxe7 22. Bb7 Rxc2 $1 {After
