[%cal Gc6d4]} 18. Nf3 Rh6 $132 {[%cal Ga5a4,Gc6a5,Ga5c4] Black's idea is to
play ...a5-a4 and ...Na5-c4. Black has a very decent play.}) 13... Qb7 $1 $146
14. Qe3 {[%cal Ga4b6] White intends to play Nb6 in order to bring the knight
back from the rim into the game.} Rb8 {[%csl Ra4] Black naturally prevents it.}
15. Nd2 Na7 $1 {With this nice maneuver, Black forces White to push b3 and
weaken the pawns.} 16. b3 (16. Qb3 $2 Nc8 $1 $17 {[%csl Ra4][%cal Gb7c6] The
