a3 $146 Nc6 16. Nb2 bxa3 17. Nc4 Qxd2 18. Rxd2 Rb8 19. Nxd6+ Bxd6 20. Rxd6 Ke7
21. Rd2 a5 {[%cal Ga5a4]} 22. Bc4 Rhc8 $132 {Black is very comfortable.}) 15...
Rb8 16. Qd4 Qc7 17. cxb4 Bxa4 18. bxa4 Qd7 $1 {Black sacrificed a pawn for the
